                    background. So these symbols will appear, just as the way you&mdash;you
                    pronounce your words appear. You don't know where you learned to pronounce words
                    the way you do because you&mdash;you inherited that or it came from your
                    early environment, and these symbols, which are Christian symbols, are a part of
