                    from. That's why I think critics read into books what the writer didn't know was
                    there, because he reads from the same background of Christian symbolism which
                    the writer unconsciously <span class="unclear tooltip" title="Text was unclear">[wrote]</span> from. And I'm sure that these
                    symbols are all there, but the writer himself don't know it till somebody points
                    them out to him. Because he is too busy simply telling about people to have to
                    hunt around to&mdash;to use symbols to tell about people with. The symbols
